title: Two Roses And A Goldenrod 1969 John Alderman, Elizabeth Knowles, Ami Paisley, Lois Ursone, Vincene Wallace + Albert Zugsmigh

sources.title: Two Roses And A Goldenrod 1969 John Alderman, Elizabeth Knowles, Ami Paisley, Lois Ursone, Vincene Wallace + Albert Zugsmigh
sources.description: Mother and daughter fight for the affection of the same man, mom's husband. Mom eventually wins by bringing in the female neighbor next door. Odd bit spliced in that seems to be an angel and a devil looking in on various sinful acts.
